## Module: Nature of Business

### Overview
This module covers key concepts in Nature of Business for the HSC business course.

### Topics
- Topic 1 in Nature of Business
- Topic 2 in Nature of Business

### Learning Outcomes

Students will develop skills to:

- Identify and explain key concepts related to Nature of Business
- Analyse and interpret information related to Nature of Business
- Apply understanding of Nature of Business to solve problems
- Evaluate arguments and perspectives related to Nature of Business
- Communicate understanding of Nature of Business using appropriate terminology

### Key Concepts

This module introduces the following key concepts:

- Fundamental principles of Nature of Business
- Core terminology and definitions
- Theoretical frameworks
- Practical applications
- Critical analysis techniques

